      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.sobLlAGQkmWcFBFx]{Magic Hack}</p>\n<p>Whenever an opponent you’re aware of casts a spell, as a reaction you can cast <em>dispel magic</em> or <em>greater dispel magic</em> in an attempt to counter the spell, even if you didn’t ready an action or select that opponent. This magic hack doesn’t allow you to cast a spell that you don’t know, and you must expend a spell slot of the appropriate level to cast <em>dispel magic</em> or <em>greater dispel magic</em> in this way. You must know <em>dispel magic</em> or <em>greater dispel magic</em> to select this magic hack.</p>"
